        <h2>
            资中筠自选集（全五册）的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 12 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5806772">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5806772/" class="title-link">天朝乌托邦</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5806772"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/wac727/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1919118-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wac727/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">寒柳</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-03-11"
      class="main-meta">2013-03-11 04:35:09</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5806772_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  资中筠被誉为真正的名媛，然而头脑中并非风花雪月，而是爱憎分明，以及对国家的忧怀。我实在纳闷，这套书竟然能够出版。她老人家的抨击，在我看来是犯了很多禁区的。实在难以写笔记，也许会被屏蔽，还是整体评论下。  资中筠一以贯之的精神是说真话，而且针砭时弊。事实上共产...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5806772/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">22有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5806772_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5806772_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5832531">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5832531/" class="title-link">读资中筠《中国教育不改变，人种都会退化》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5832531"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

