        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="23088742">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/eagleeye/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u45205420-5.jpg" alt=" Eagleeye" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23088742/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23088742/" class="">跨世纪中国人将如何自处？</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/eagleeye/" class=" " title=" Eagleeye"> Eagleeye</a>
                (潜龙勿用)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23088742">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我们最大的敌人是自己不争气，是国内弥漫的腐化和种种严重的弊端。当务之急是切实加强内功，兴利除弊，“把自己的事情办好”（邓小平）。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-11 10:45</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                我们最大的敌人是自己不争气，是国内弥漫的腐化和种种严重的弊端。当务之急是切实加强内功，兴利除弊，“把自己的事情办好”（邓小平）。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

